This workflow does not deploy code.
It enforces design integrity.
9. Neutral Investor-Safe Description
BuzzIntell™ is a non-authoritative intelligence layer that improves security decisions by separating perception from power. It enables safer access systems by ensuring intelligence cannot authorize itself and execution cannot escalate itself.
10. Final Positioning Statement
BuzzIntell is not a product that “controls.”
It is a system that clarifies.
That restraint is the value.